if it came to it.
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[2]Ah, it looks like we can climb the stairs.
Would you like to go up the stairs?
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[3]*pant* *pant*... Climbing up 30 floors is really tiring...
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[3]I feel like my stamina is about half gone...

\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[4]If the elevator isn't working, I guess we have no choice but
to use the stairs...
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[10]...I have a bad feeling about this.

When Kohane-chan has that feeling, she's often right. If it
bothers you, maybe we should use the \C[2]stairs\C[0]
instead of the elevator.
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[1]Puppy! Come hereyour master is waiting for you.
It seems there are no more traps in this area.

So you've made it this far. As expected of a magical girl
from the Guardians.
Really... You're such a disconcerting girl...
Anyway, I can't let you go any further from here.
Mmm... I guess there's no helping it...
As if I would say that!!

Until our objective is achieved, we cannot allow you to
interfere!!

\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[2]Right, right, I want to know what this objective of yours
is.

Heh, there's no need to explain, you'll understand soon
enough.
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[4]That means... the plan is already well underway, huh.

Hmph, you already know about the \C[2]Guardians
Annihilation Plan\C[0]? Yes, the preparations for our plan
to annihilate the Guardianswho unfairly control ability
users and prevent them from using their powers freelyare in
the final stages!

\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[11]That's quite a dangerous plan. But I think it's impossible
to annihilate the Guardians...

Heh, we'll see about that. Underestimate our power and
you'll regret it.

\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[2]It must be a really amazing plan then.\FaceIndex[1] But I've
got some good info now. The \C[2]Guardians Annihilation
Plan\C[0], right Hisana-chan?

Kohane-chan, you're really good at letting the enemy's guard
down. I see... so that's the Liberators' aim.
Could it be... you... knew nothing?
And yet you came here all by yourself?

To think I've given information to such a thoughtless
girl... How careless of me...
Well, it's not like you can blame him for thinking that.

Grr, anyway, I cannot let you proceed until the preparations
are complete! Here I come!

You're a persistent girl. No matter how many times you come,
the result will be the same! Let's go!

This is a defeat scene you've seen before. Would you like to
see it again?

However... I am the weakest among the Four Heavenly Kings...
Be sure to stay on your guard!

Then let's activate the elevator at that security center
over there.

It's a defeat scene you've seen before. Would you like to
view it again?

\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[2]We can't even use the stairs... I thought we could run up
them if it came to that.
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[2]Ah, it looks like we can climb the stairs here.
Would you like to climb the stairs?
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[3]I feel like my energy's been cut in half...

\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[4]If the elevator isn't working, I guess we have no choice but
to use the stairs...
\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[10]...I have a bad feeling about this.

When Kohane-chan has that feeling, she's often right. If it
bothers you, maybe we should use the \C[2]stairs\C[0]
instead of the elevator.

<center>If you are defeated in the upcoming battle, you will
transition to a defeat H-scene. If you do not wish to
experience the defeat H-scene, we recommend saving your
game.Defeat H-scenes will be added to recollection just by
winning the battle.</center>
<center>The next encounter will be a boss battle.</center>
Bind Guard prevented the restraint trap!
That was close... We need to be careful.
Suddenly, ropes appeared and I was restrained!

\PartyFace[1]\FaceIndex[0]Phew... That was close. We really need to be careful of
traps, huh?

You can fully recover HP and MP. Would you like to fully
recover?

You can fully recover HP and MP. Would you like to fully
recover?
Seraphier-sama... she always looks so cool...
What, are you also a fan of Seraphier-sama?

As expected, even a child like you can feel the charm of
Seraphier-sama.

But I refuse to share my adoration, so please don't talk to
me too much.

To not understand the charm of Seraphier-sama... how
childish.

It's not just her beauty, Seraphier-sama's abilities are
also incredible. She moves faster than anyone, and always
attacks first \C[2]it's just too cool!\C[0]

But since I refuse to share my adoration, even if you come
to like Seraphier-sama, please never talk to me about it.

Seraphier-sama... Even your departing figure is as cool as
the wind...
